    "description": "<p>Aerospec Supplies Pte Ltd provides our clients licensed aircraft engineers, aircraft technicians and all other aviation personnel.</p>\n\n<p>We have been in the business of manpower solutions since 1990s and having served the Aviation industry for over 20 years, Aerospec Supplies Pte Ltd has in-depth industry knowledge and professional understanding of your recruitment requirements.We are able to provide you with local and international expertise in that area for contract and permanent placement according to your requirements.</p>\n\n<p>Whether your requirement is short, medium or long term, seasonal, scheduled and/or unscheduled, Aerospec Supplies Pte Ltd can deliver the expertise. </p>\n",
